Package com.hf.fundamental.dao

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IdentityDAO
    The IdentityDAO interface allows to define reusable behaviors for DAOs
    UserDAO
    The UserDAO interface allows to define reusable behavior for DAOs.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DAOFactory
    The DAOFactory class allows to instantiate concrete objects for DAOs in the application.
    DerbyDAOFactory
    The DerbyDAOFactory allows to instantiate concrete objects for DerbyDAO in the application.
    DerbyIdentityDAO
    The DerbyIdentityDAO class implements the abstract class SQLIdentityDAO.
    DerbyUserDAO
    The DerbyUserDAO class implements the SQLUserDAO.
    SqlDAO
    The SQLDAO class defines the methods needed to establish and close the connection with a database.
    SQLIdentityDAO
    The SQLIdentityDAO class has the Identity CRUD methods implementation for databases.
    SQLUserDAO
    The SQLUserDAO class has the User CRUD methods implementation for databases.
    Storage
    The Storage class defines the types of storage available.
    XMLDAOFactory
    The XMLDAOFactory class allows to instantiate concrete objects for DAOs in the application.
    XMLIdentityDAO
    The XMLIdentityDAO class implements the Identity object CRUD methods for Identity.
    XMLUserDAO
    The XMLUserDAO class implements the User authenticate method for User.
